release_note: Fixed a minor bug that prevented users from adding a new journal entry

v1.6.2 Teeny tiny update with a few bundled fixes : Fixed theme behavior and components effected by theming Added a new scroll to bottom or top button to help navigate longer lists of journal entries Fixed issue that would prevent users from viewing the bottom of a long text input field Improved sign in flow
Fixed bottom border causing text to render off screen for some users.
Fixed theme not saving between app sessions and added iPad support.
Updated UI brings Quill to match iOS 14 s design style! This update makes Quill easier to use as well as improves user login time and experience. Enjoy!
